  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Integral Ecology in the Colombian Amazon</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This grant funds the social programme of a Catholic diocese in one of the areas of Colombia most affected by the conflict. This project is the continuation of COL196. The new 2021-2023 strategy of the dioceses will continue to develop the capacity of the parish groups (EPPAS) bringing a stronger focus on integral ecology and Care for Our Common Home in the context of the Amazon Synod and Querida Amazonia with the aim of developing and implementing a plan for the protection of the Amazon in the area of intervention, led by the local communities. Children play a key role in this. It also seeks to strengthen participation in the democratic process thorough local advocacy initiatives and developing local actions.  A specific component will focus on communication.</narrative>
  </description>
